    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talebuilder 是一款以卡牌为核心的战术棋盘战斗游戏。每一页都会塑造书中的故事，将叙事紧密结合，并通过英雄、神器和多样化的能力卡构建战斗策略，迎接最终章节的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从多种英雄中组建你的主角小队……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/eba16267267da1b6437883b022e29048.avif?t=1769958102\" alt=\"\"width=1400 height=700 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >…迎战王国的众多入侵者……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/25411f2f34186c5b4f2a6ff1b5fdca14.avif?t=1769958102\" alt=\"\"width=1400 height=700 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >…使用数十张技能卡牌……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/b7178c08a2b4b948d2a030032ff2d7d2.avif?t=1769958102\" alt=\"\"width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >…在快节奏的战术战斗中操控战场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/5c3ddd4ed3078fdf6cc459cb4df7cb1b.poster.avif?t=1769958102\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/5c3ddd4ed3078fdf6cc459cb4df7cb1b.webm?t=1769958102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/5c3ddd4ed3078fdf6cc459cb4df7cb1b.mp4?t=1769958102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/c128c115e9160c03948c3f51f206bd32.poster.avif?t=1769958102\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/c128c115e9160c03948c3f51f206bd32.webm?t=1769958102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/c128c115e9160c03948c3f51f206bd32.mp4?t=1769958102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/ff0bcc3666eb497c8ad4651ee9565343.poster.avif?t=1769958102\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/ff0bcc3666eb497c8ad4651ee9565343.webm?t=1769958102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/ff0bcc3666eb497c8ad4651ee9565343.mp4?t=1769958102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讲述你如何击败书中的反派，寻找盟友，并将他们的故事与目标编织在一起。将优秀的叙事以元叙事的方式转化为胜利的力量！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/e7bc7d2c59e0ad7e005ff0d42bafa8e4.poster.avif?t=1769958102\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038090/extras/e7bc7d2c59e0ad7e005ff0d42bafa8e4.mp4?t=1769958102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
